										<p class="text-blue-600">Accessibility Advocate & AI Professional</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<blockquote class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">
									"The course opened up entirely new creative possibilities for me. AI has become an incredible tool for amplifying what I can achieve, regardless of my visual impairment."
								</blockquote>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Shawn, who is blind, leveraged our Prompt Engineering course to gain new career skills and unlock creative possibilities, demonstrating that our approach to augmented intelligence creates opportunities for everyone.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="space-y-6">
							<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
								<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fortune 500 Impact</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									A major chemical manufacturer used our courses to train 80% of their IT workforce, with 200 employees earning advanced AI badges.
								</p>
							</div>

							<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
								<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Government Adoption</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									The U.S. Federal Acquisition Institute created official AI credentials for federal employees using our content.
								</p>
							</div>

							<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
								<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Global Reach</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Over 1,000 companies worldwide are using our courses to upskill their workforce across all industries.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Corporate Training -->
		<section id="corporate" class="py-20 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
						Corporate Training Solutions
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						Transform your workforce with AI skills that drive real business results. Trusted by 1,000+ companies worldwide.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Enterprise Training Programs</h3>
						<div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
							<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Customized Curriculum</h4>
									<p class="text-gray-600">Tailored training programs designed for your industry and specific use cases</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
