							</div>
							<div class="text-center">
								<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">1,000+</div>
								<div class="text-gray-700">Companies Served</div>
							</div>
							<div class="text-center">
								<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-2">100+</div>
								<div class="text-gray-700">Countries Reached</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
							Our corporate training programs deliver measurable ROI through improved productivity, faster innovation cycles, and enhanced competitive positioning in the AI-driven marketplace.
						</p>
						<a href="https://www.coursera.org/vanderbilt" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
